{"title":"孩子（外一首）","authors":["杨灵芝"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":7,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨灵芝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你奔跑的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈说你是在飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为，你那美丽的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣裳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是妈妈眼里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你干净的脸蛋儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是妈妈的明月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑夜里伴着妈妈的甜梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若是你将脸蛋儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抹脏了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就好比飘来一朵黑云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遮掩了妈妈的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你在一张"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的纸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用红笔画一个太阳在天上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和你自己的模样在地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈就知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，懂事了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为，早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和妈妈一起睁开了眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏的浏阳河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏的浏阳河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳和月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温存地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在涟漪上亲吻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖延着离去的夕阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知是焦急的等待"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是这温存的气氛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她那颗跳动的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染红了天边的云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东边的月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早早地跳出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缩短了离别的时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那缕缕的情丝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却随着九曲的河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延伸……延伸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传递着他们彼此的体温……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}